Package com.zeitheron.hammercore.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IHammerCoreAPI
    Represents API to be used.
    ILog
    Simple logging interface for external APIs
    INoItemBlock
    Disables item for block (only applied to Hammer Core's multipart block.
    IProcess
    The process API that may run each server/client tick.
    ITileBlock<T extends net.minecraft.tileentity.TileEntity>
    Allows SimpleRegistration to register a TileEntity class that this block contains, automatically.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APILoader
    Allows modder to check for external APIs.
    AttributeModifierAtomic
    The attribute modifier that may be implemented at any point in time.
    CustomMonsterAttributes
    Few custom attributes that Hammer Core implements for use.
    EnergyUnit
    This class helps convert energy values across different power systems
    GameRules
    A complete control over Game Rule API
    GameRules.GameRuleEntry
    The class for the game rule.
    RequiredDeps
    Gather all required IHammerCoreAPIs.
    WrappedFMLLog
    Implementation for ILog.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GameRules.ValueType  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    HammerCoreAPI
    Allows any class to be defined as an instance for API between HammerCore and used class.
